name: Asia with Multi-Standard 20190902
description:
by teshnakamura 2019

https://teshnakamura.com/asia-with-multi-standard-20190902/

A Java program, which I coded, draws Asias (somethings self-organizing) all day automatically with random parameters, it takes around 10 mins for an Asia; about 140 Asias a day.
Some look pretty cool while others are boring. I choose "Asia of the day" in those 140 and post it on Instagram(@teshnakamura) every day.
